@{PARD}
@{B}Draconian, Rosak Habitat/Society:@{UB}@{PAR}

Because of their superior abilities, Rosaks are easily adaptable to all
environments, thought they may seek to keep their true nature hidden for their
own protection. They love all treasure, especially magical weapons and platinum
coins.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

