@{PARD}
@{B}Draconian, Rosak Ecology:@{UB}@{PAR}

Rosaks have a cumpulsive need to bring about the destruction of their evil
cousins. There is no restriction to what a Rosak will eat, though most prefer
meat and wine. They will consume other alcohols if they must, to keep up
appearances, but will avoid them at other times. The use of a Rosak scale in
addition to the regular components of any fire based spell will increase the
effectiveness of the spell by one level (i.e. a 5th level wizard could cast a 6
die fireball). The scale is consumed even if the other components are not.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

