@{PARD}
@{B}Draconian, Rosak History:@{UB}@{PAR}

The existence of the Rosak draconians went largely unnoticed until very
recently. According to the great historian, Astinius of Palanthas, they were
created by Sorian, a renegade magic-user and the Brass Dragon Brillianta, during
the War of the Lance as an attempt to turn the tide against the armies of the
evil dragons. No one is sure just how many were created, but the number couldn't
have been many for Sorian was killed during the war defending his homeland from
invaders.@{PAR}

